The paper deals with smoothed analysis in unsupervised learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the analysis of algorithms, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also deals with matrix ensembles, which is a topic in cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Finally, the paper involves the design of algorithms for unsupervised learning, which is a topic in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
